; Coverage test for xact.cc line 758-759 (xact_t copy constructor)
; Tests the copy constructor via --related which uses copy_xact()
; in the related_posts filter to create temporary transaction copies.

2024/03/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --related
24-Mar-01 Groceries             Assets:Cash                 $-10.00      $-10.00
end test
